VYDBUr MShH 'aL-Ur'aShY HMTVTh LBNY YShUr'aL L'aMUr ZH HDBUr 'aShUr TShVH YHVH.
'aYSh KY-YDUr NDUr LYHVH 'aV-HShB'y ShB'yH L'aSUr 'aSUr 'yL-NPhShV L'a YChL DBUrV KKL-HYTSh'a MPhYV Y'yShH.
V'aShH KY-ThDUr NDUr LYHVH V'aSUrH 'aSUr BBYTh 'aBYH BN'yUrYH.
VShM'y 'aBYH 'aTh-NDUrH V'aSUrH 'aShUr 'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH VHChUrYSh LH 'aBYH VQMV KL-NDUrYH VKL-'aSUr 'aShUr-'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH YQVM.
V'aM-HNY'a 'aBYH 'aThH BYVM ShM'yV KL-NDUrYH V'aSUrYH 'aShUr-'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH L'a YQVM VYHVH YSLCh-LH KY-HNY'a 'aBYH 'aThH.
V'aM-HYV ThHYH L'aYSh VNDUrYH 'yLYH 'aV MBT'a ShPhThYH 'aShUr 'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH.
VShM'y 'aYShH BYVM ShM'yV VHChUrYSh LH VQMV NDUrYH V'aSUrH 'aShUr-'aSUrH 'yL- NPhShH YQMV.
V'aM BYVM ShM'y 'aYShH YNY'a 'aVThH VHPhUr 'aTh-NDUrH 'aShUr 'yLYH V'aTh MBT'a ShPhThYH 'aShUr 'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH VYHVH YSLCh-LH.
VNDUr 'aLMNH VGUrVShH KL 'aShUr-'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH YQVM 'yLYH.
V'aM-BYTh 'aYShH NDUrH 'aV-'aSUrH 'aSUr 'yL-NPhShH BShB'yH.
VShM'y 'aYShH VHChUrSh LH L'a HNY'a 'aThH VQMV KL-NDUrYH VKL-'aSUr 'aShUr- 'aSUrH 'yL-NPhShH YQVM.
V'aM-HPhUr YPhUr 'aThM 'aYShH BYVM ShM'yV KL-MVTSh'a ShPhThYH LNDUrYH VL'aSUr NPhShH L'a YQVM 'aYShH HPhUrM VYHVH YSLCh-LH.
KL-NDUr VKL-ShB'yTh 'aSUr L'yNTh NPhSh 'aYShH YQYMNV V'aYShH YPhUrNV.
V'aM-HChUrSh YChUrYSh LH 'aYShH MYVM 'aL-YVM VHQYM 'aTh-KL-NDUrYH 'aV 'aTh- KL-'aSUrYH 'aShUr 'yLYH HQYM 'aThM KY-HChUrSh LH BYVM ShM'yV.
V'aM-HPhUr YPhUr 'aThM 'aChUrY ShM'yV VNSh'a 'aTh-'yVNH.
'aLH HChQYM 'aShUr TShVH YHVH 'aTh-MShH BYN 'aYSh L'aShThV BYN-'aB LBThV BN'yUrYH BYTh 'aBYH.
